==Influence== The philosopher [[Mark D. Jordan]], writing in ''[[The Oxford Companion to Philosophy]]'' (1995), stated that ''An Introduction to the Philosophy of Religion'' helped popularized the term "[[philosophy of religion]]" in English.<ref>[[#Jor95|Jordan 1995]]. p. 759.</ref>
