{{Infobox book | name = Beyond Selflessness: Reading Nietzsche's Genealogy | image = File:Beyond Selflessness.jpg | image_size = 200px | author = [[Christopher Janaway]] | country = | language = English | subject = [[Friedrich Nietzsche]] | publisher = [[Oxford University Press]] | pub_date = 2007 | media_type = Print ([[Hardcover]] and [[Paperback]]) | pages = 296 | isbn = 978-0199570850 | dewey = | congress = | oclc = }} '''''Beyond Selflessness: Reading Nietzsche's Genealogy''''' is a philosophical examination of the work of [[Friedrich Nietzsche]] in ''[[On the Genealogy of Morality]]'' (1887). The monograph was released by [[Christopher Janaway]] in 2007 as part of his series examining the work of Nietzsche.<ref name="amazon1">{{Cite book|title=Beyond Selflessness: Reading Nietzsche's Genealogy: Amazon.co.uk: Christopher Janaway: Books |publisher=Amazon.co.uk |date= |id= {{ASIN|019957085X|country=uk}} }}</ref>
